  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Final Outpost is a survival strategy base-builder. You lead the last survivors of the apocalypse. Assign roles, craft tools, and manage resources carefully. Construct buildings, level up your citizens, and fortify your town against hordes of zombies. How many days can you survive? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/a6dc5613bc06000d29e47b47b7978fbc.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 10+ job roles for each of your citizens, and watch them get to work! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/ebb8fd2c9bfd4c0fd28725ecb6f457a8.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct and upgrade 12+ building types and expand your sprawling settlement. Build vital resource storage, production buildings and housing for new survivors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/d1c55812d5c5240df29bd6684f2b8ac6.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/d1c55812d5c5240df29bd6684f2b8ac6.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/d1c55812d5c5240df29bd6684f2b8ac6.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/fd37e778e3fe58f0a6bd34b189670932.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deck out your defences to keep 5+ zombie types away from your walls. Start out with a single knife and progress to mowing down hordes with machine guns, crossbows and snipers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/67c9dbfc3276b331217f38d1eafa29a6.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/67c9dbfc3276b331217f38d1eafa29a6.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/67c9dbfc3276b331217f38d1eafa29a6.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/c31d407e55b7653048134ecd7790d7d6.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed your hungry citizens as your Outpost expands. Begin farming wheat in your fields to overcome the dwindling deer population outside your walls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/03bc58beb3defe3fcf50e3ca550b8a9e.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/03bc58beb3defe3fcf50e3ca550b8a9e.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/03bc58beb3defe3fcf50e3ca550b8a9e.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e60ea7b3c2eaba2317b474f819adbeca.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive harsh droughts, cold winters, and unforgiving thunderstorms with simulated weather and seasons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e246b2f1129e5c7ca3f9808859629e24.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e246b2f1129e5c7ca3f9808859629e24.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/e246b2f1129e5c7ca3f9808859629e24.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/4b0d6d2a228cfcbfbdc2de589f27c2c2.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your citizens’ skills to gather, defend and repair more efficiently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/759ad903cf2f15afa446e7d512d6e2c4.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/759ad903cf2f15afa446e7d512d6e2c4.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/759ad903cf2f15afa446e7d512d6e2c4.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Final Outpost is a survival strategy base-builder. You lead the last survivors of the apocalypse. Assign roles, craft tools, and manage resources carefully. Construct buildings, level up your citizens, and fortify your town against hordes of zombies. How many days can you survive? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/a6dc5613bc06000d29e47b47b7978fbc.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 10+ job roles for each of your citizens, and watch them get to work! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.poster.avif?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.webm?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/3fc81176e5d81a6be55748bf63f435f0.mp4?t=1765278401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066310/extras/ebb8fd2c9bfd4c0fd28725ecb6f457a8.webp?t=1765278401\" width=630 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct and upgrade 12+ building types and expand your sprawling settlement. Build vital resource storage, production buildings and housing for new survivors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat